EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
SCOTLAND-WEST COAST.
HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS.
DNC 19.
1. HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS 251000Z TO 252000Z OCT
   WITHIN 15 MILES OF 57-22.6N 007-59.5W.
   VESSELS INTENDING TO ENTER AREA SHOULD CONTACT
   HEBRIDES RANGE CONTROL ON VHF CH 16
   OR PHONE: 187 060 4449 FOR ADVICE.
2. CANCEL HYDROLANT 2603/15(GEN), PRN 23 RESTORED.
3. CANCEL THIS MSG 252100Z OCT 15.
